==Useful Info==
'''Martyred shades''' are monsters summoned by the [[Martyr's Knell]] spell. Their main purpose is to [[Injury Bond|absorb damage]], shielding your allies. Martyred shades regenerate health quickly, but have poor defenses and relatively low maximum HP. Upon death, a martyred shade turns into a [[flayed ghost]].

==Tips & Tricks==

==History==
